#, no-c-format
msgid "Move the word to the \"Unused\" terminal."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Because you (hopefully) don't use the terminal \"Unused\" in your grammar, the word will no longer be considered for recognition. In fact, it will be removed from the active vocabulary before compiling the model because no grammar sentence references it."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you want to use the terminal \"Unused\" in your grammar, you can of course use a different terminal for unused words. Just set the terminal through the <link linkend=\"edit_word\">Edit word</link> dialog."
