#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1411
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the word completely but keeps the associated samples. Whenever you add another word with the same word name the samples will be re-associated."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Be careful with this option as the new word you add again might be transcribed differently and this difference can not be taken into account automatically (simon will then try to force the new transcription on the old recordings during the model compilation)."
