#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Just remove the word. All the recordings containing the word will be removed too."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option leaves no trace of neither the word itself nor the associated samples."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
