#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2528
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default the input number plugin uses numbers to select the individual digits and a couple of control words. To use the input number plugin, make sure that your language and acoustic model contains and allows for the following \"sentences\":"
msgstr ""

