#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next to the tabs that hold the keys of your set, the keyboard my also show special keys like Ctrl, Shift, etc. Those keys are provided as voice inteface commands and are displayed regardless of what tab of the set is currently active."
